<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to KarirKalyan</title>
  </head>
  <body style="margin:0; padding:0; background-color:#f4f1ea; font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; color:#1a1a2e;">
    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#f4f1ea; padding:32px 16px;">
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="max-width:520px; background-color:#ffffff; border:1px solid #d8d3c4;">
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:28px 32px 8px 32px;">
                <p style="margin:0; font-size:12px; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#6b6b7b;">KarirKalyan</p>
                <h1 style="margin:12px 0 0 0; font-size:22px; font-weight:600; color:#1a1a2e;">
                  Welcome aboard <span style="color:#2b4eff;">👋</span>
                </h1>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:16px 32px 8px 32px; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6; color:#3a3a4a;">
                <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;">
                  Thanks for signing up. KarirKalyan keeps your job search organised — track every
                  application through a clear pipeline, keep an audit trail of every status change,
                  and get a follow-up nudge when a recruiter goes quiet.
                </p>
                <p style="margin:0 0 8px 0; font-weight:600; color:#1a1a2e;">Get started:</p>
                <ul style="margin:0 0 16px 0; padding-left:20px;">
                  <li style="margin-bottom:6px;">Add your first application — company, role, and the job posting URL.</li>
                  <li style="margin-bottom:6px;">Attach the exact resume and cover letter you sent.</li>
                  <li style="margin-bottom:6px;">Set a follow-up date and we'll email you when it's due.</li>
                </ul>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:16px 32px 28px 32px;">
                <a href="<%= @new_application_url %>" style="display:inline-block; background-color:#2b4eff; color:#f4f1ea; text-decoration:none; font-size:14px; font-weight:500; padding:11px 22px; margin-right:8px;">
                  Add your first application
                </a>
                <a href="<%= @dashboard_url %>" style="display:inline-block; color:#2b4eff; text-decoration:none; font-size:14px; font-weight:500; padding:11px 4px;">
                  Go to dashboard →
                </a>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
          <p style="max-width:520px; margin:16px auto 0 auto; font-size:12px; line-height:1.5; color:#9a9aa8;">
            You're receiving this because you created a KarirKalyan account with this address.
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
